# Capabilities Routing

When delegating work, spawn the matching subagent from `.cursor/agents/`:

| Task domain | Subagent | Paths |
|-------------|----------|-------|
| Planning / scoping | `planner` | whole repo |
| Engine, APIs, models, tests | `core-implementer` | `BoskePulseCore/**` |
| Menu bar UI, AppModel, Keychain | `app-implementer` | `BoskePulse/**` |
| WidgetKit views, timeline | `widget-implementer` | `BoskePulseWidget/**` |
| Post-change validation | `verifier` | whole repo |

## Detected layout

```
boske-pulse/
├── BoskePulseCore/     # Swift Package — shared engine + tests
├── BoskePulse/         # Menu bar app (SwiftUI)
├── BoskePulseWidget/   # WidgetKit extension
├── Config/             # JSON topology (example committed)
├── scripts/            # setup.sh, render-brand-icons.swift
├── project.yml         # XcodeGen
└── docs/work/active/   # Active plan + checklist
```

## Skills

- `/run-core-tests` — execute `make test`
- `/add-pulse-feature` — planner → implementers → verifier workflow
